\c 12
\s UJesu uxwayisa abafundi bakhe
\p
\v 1 Kusenjalo sezibuthene izigidi zexuku, baze banyathelana, waqala ukukhuluma labafundi bakhe kuqala\x + Seb. 24.18. 26.12.\x*: Lina xwayani imvubelo yabaFarisi\x + Mat. 16.6,12. Mark. 8.15. Luka 17.3.\x*, eyikuzenzisa\x + Mat. 23.28.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Njalo kakukho okumbomboziweyo, okungayikwembulwa, lokufihliweyo, okungayikwaziwa\x + Mat. 10.26-33. Mark. 4.22. Luka 8.17.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho loba yini eliyikhuluma emnyameni izazwakala ekukhanyeni; lelikukhulume endlebeni ezindlini zensitha\x + 11.24. Mat. 6.6.\x* kuzamenyezelwa phezu kwezindlu\x + 2 Sam. 11.2.\x*.
\s Omele ukwesatshwa
\p
\v 4 Njalo ngithi kini bangane bami: Lingabesabi ababulala umzimba, njalo emva kwalokho bengelakho ukwenza olunye ulutho\x + Joha. 15.13-15.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa ngizalitshengisa elifanele ukumesaba: Mesabeni lowo othi esebulele abe lamandla okuphosela esihogweni; yebo, ngithi kini: Mesabeni yena\x + Mat. 3.7. Luka 3.7. 6.47. Seb. 9.16.20.35.\x*.
\v 6 Kazithengiswa yini intaka ezinhlanu ngendibilitshi ezimbili? Kakukhohlakali lanye yazo phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 10.29.\x*.
\v 7 Kanti lenwele zekhanda lenu zibaliwe zonke. Ngakho lingesabi; liyazedlula intaka ezinengi.
\p
\v 8 Njalo ngithi kini: Wonke loba ngubani ongivuma phambi kwabantu, iNdodana yomuntu layo izamvuma phambi kwengilosi zikaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 25.31.\x*;
\v 9 kodwa ongiphika phambi kwabantu uzaphikwa phambi kwengilosi zikaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 25.31.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Laye wonke okhuluma ilizwi elimelana leNdodana yomuntu, uzathethelelwa; kodwa lowo ohlambaza uMoya oNgcwele kayikuthethelelwa\x + Mat. 12.31.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Njalo nxa belisa emasinagogeni\x + Mat. 10.19. Mark. 13.11. Luka 21.14.\x* la\add ku\add*babusi\x + Roma 8.38.\x*\x + Efe. 3.10; 6.12. Kol. 1.16. Tit. 3.1. Luka 20.20. Kol. 2.10.\x* leziphathamandla\x + Roma 13.1. 1 Pet. 3.22.\x*\x + Efe. 3.10; 6.12. Kol. 1.16. Tit. 3.1. Luka 20.20. Kol. 2.10.\x*, lingakhathazeki ukuthi lizaphendula njani kumbe liphenduleni, kumbe lizakhulumani\x + Mat. 10.20.\x*;
\v 12 ngoba uMoya oNgcwele uzalifundisa ngalelohola izinto e\add li\add*fanele ukuzikhuluma.
\s Umfanekiso womlimi onothileyo
\p
\v 13 Futhi omunye wexuku wathi kuye: Mfundisi, akutshele umfowethu abelane lami ilifa.
\v 14 Kodwa wathi kuye: Ndoda\x + Roma 2.1,3; 9.20.\x*, ngubani ongimise \add ukuthi ngibe\add* ngumahluleli loba umehlukanisi phezu kwenu\x + Joha. 8.11. Eks. 2.14. Seb. 7.27,35.\x*?
\v 15 Wasesithi kubo: Nanzelelani liqaphele ubuhwaba, ngoba impilo yomuntu kayikho ebunengini bezinto alazo\x + 1 Tim. 6.6-11.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Wasebatshela umfanekiso, esithi: Insimu yomuntu othile onothileyo yathela kakhulu;
\v 17 wasenakana ngaphakathi kwakhe\x + 3.15.\x*, esithi: Ngizakwenza njani, ngoba kangilandawo lapho engingabuthela khona izithelo zami\x + 11.23.\x*?
\v 18 Wasesithi: Ngizakwenza lokhu; ngizadiliza iziphala zami, ngakhe ezinkulu\x + 12.24. 3.17.\x*, ngibuthele khona izilimo zami zonke lempahla yami\x + 11.23.\x*,
\v 19 besengisithi kumphefumulo wami: Mphefumulo, ulempahla ezinengi ezibekelwe iminyaka eminengi; phumula, udle, unathe\x + Tshu. 11.9. 1 Kor. 15.32. Jak. 5.5. Tshu. 2.24.\x*, uthokoze\x + 15.23.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kuye: Siphukuphuku\x + Jer. 17.11. Jak. 4.14.\x*, ngalobubusuku umphefumulo wakho uzabizwa\f + \fk uzabizwa: \fl Gr. \fq bazabiza.\f* kuwe\x + Jobe 27.8. Hlab. 52.7.\x*; pho izinto ozilungisileyo zizakuba ngezikabani\x + Hlab. 39.6.\x*?
\v 21 Kunjalo-ke kozibekela inotho\x + Mat. 6.19,20.\x*, kodwa enganothanga kuNkulunkulu\x + 6.24. 12.33. 1 Tim. 6.18,19. Jak. 2.5.\x*.
\s Ukukhathazeka, lokuthemba kuNkulunkulu
\p
\v 22 Wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: Ngakho ngithi kini: Lingakhathaleli impilo yenu, ukuthi lizakudlani; loba umzimba, ukuthi lizakwembathani.
\v 23 Impilo yedlula ukudla, lomzimba isembatho\x + Mat. 6.25-33.\x*.
\v 24 Qaphelisisani amawabayi, ukuthi kawahlanyeli, njalo kawavuni\x + Jobe 38.41.\x*, kawalasiphala\x + 12.24. 3.17.\x* loba isilulu\x + 12.3.\x*, kanti uNkulunkulu uyawondla; lina lizedlula kangakanani\x + Jobe 38.41.\x* inyoni?
\v 25 Njalo nguwuphi kini \add ongathi\add* ngokuphiseka engezelele ingalo ibenye\x + 12.26.\x* ebudeni bakhe\x + 2.52.\x*?
\v 26 Ngakho nxa lingelamandla okwenza into encinyane, liphisekelani ngokunye?
\v 27 Qaphelisani imiduze ukuthi ikhula njani; kayitshikatshiki, kayiphothi, kodwa ngithi kini: LoSolomoni ebucwazicwazini bakhe bonke wayengembathiswanga njengomunye wayo.
\v 28 Njalo uba uNkulunkulu esembathisa ngokunjalo utshani obukhona lamuhla egangeni, kuthi kusasa buphoswa eziko, \add uza\add*l\add embathisa\add* ngokukhulu kangakanani, lina abokholo oluncinyane\x + 12.26.\x*?
\v 29 Lani-ke lingadingi elizakudla lelizakunatha; njalo lingakhathazeki.
\v 30 Ngoba konke lokhu izizwe zomhlaba ziyakudinga; kodwa uYihlo uyazi ukuthi liyaziswela lezizinto.
\v 31 Kodwa dingani umbuso kaNkulunkulu, njalo zonke lezizinto zizakwengezelelwa kini.
\v 32 Lingesabi\x + Isa. 41.10,13,14; 43.5; 42.2.\x*, mhlambi omncinyane\x + Zek. 13.7. Joha. 21.15-17. Seb. 20.28. Isa. 40.11.\x*; ngoba kuyikuthanda kukaYihlo\x + Efe. 1.5,9. Mat. 11.25,26. Luka 10.21.\x* ukulinika umbuso\x + Mat. 25.34.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Thengisani impahla zenu\x + Mat. 19.21.\x* liphe izipho\x + 11.41.\x*. Lizenzele\x + 16.9.\x* imixhaka engagugiyo\x + 10.4.\x*, impahla eligugu engapheliyo emazulwini, lapho okungasondeli isela khona\x + 12.21. Mat. 6.20.\x*, lenundu engoni khona\x + 12.21. Mat. 6.20.\x*;
\v 34 ngoba lapho okukhona impahla yenu eligugu, izakuba khona lapho lenhliziyo yenu\x + Mat. 6.21.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wenceku ethembekileyo
\p
\v 35 Inkalo zenu kazihlale zibotshiwe\x + 1 Kho. 18.46.\x*, lezibane \add zenu\add* zibhebha\x + Mat. 25.7,8.\x*;
\v 36 lani libe njengabantu abalindele inkosi yabo, lapho izabuya ivela emtshadweni\x + Mat. 22.2.\x*, ukuze, nxa ifika iqoqoda, bahle bayivulele.
\v 37 Zibusisiwe lezozinceku\x + Mat. 24.46.\x*, okuzakuthi inkosi nxa ifika izifice zilindile\x + Mat. 24.42.\x*; ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Izabhinca\x + 12.35. 17.8. Joha. 13.4.\x*, izihlalise ekudleni, isondele izisebenzele\x + 22.27. 17.7,8.\x*.
\v 38 Njalo nxa ifika ngomlindo wesibili\x + Eks. 14.24.\x*, kumbe ifika ngomlindo wesithathu\x + Eks. 14.24.\x*, futhi i\add zi\add*fice \add zi\add*njalo\x + Mat. 24.46.\x*, zibusisiwe lezozinceku.
\v 39 Kodwa yazini lokhu, ukuthi uba umninindlu ebelazi ihola isela elizafika ngalo\x + 12.39,40,42-46, Mat. 24.43-51.\x*, ubezalinda\x + Mat. 24.42.\x*, futhi ubengayikuvuma ukuthi indlu yakhe ifohlelwe.
\v 40 Ngakho lani-ke hlalani lilungile\x + 12.47.\x*; ngoba ngehola elingalicabangeliyo iNdodana yomuntu izafika\x + Mark. 13.33. Luka 21.34,36.\x*.
\p
\v 41 UPetro wasesithi kuye: Nkosi, uwutshela thina lumfanekiso\x + 12.47.\x*, kumbe labo bonke yini\x + 12.48.\x*?
\v 42 INkosi yasisithi: Pho ngubani umphathi wezinceku othembekileyo lohlakaniphileyo, inkosi ezambeka phezu kwabendlu yayo, ukuze a\add ba\add*nike isabelo \add sabo\add* sokudla ngesikhathi esifaneleyo\x + 16.1.\x*?
\v 43 Ibusisiwe leyonceku, okuzakuthi inkosi yayo nxa ifika iyifice isenza njalo.
\v 44 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Izayibeka phezu kwakho konke elakho.
\v 45 Kodwa nxa leyonceku isithi enhliziyweni yayo: Inkosi yami iphuzile ukubuya; njalo ibisiqala ukutshaya izinceku lezincekukazi, lokudla lokunatha lokudakwa,
\v 46 inkosi yaleyonceku izafika ngosuku enga\add yi\add*lindele ngalo, langehola engalaziyo; izayiquma phakathi, izanika isabelo sayo lalabo abangathembekanga\x + Isam. 21.8. Mat. 24.51.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Laleyonceku ebisazi intando yenkosi yayo\x + 12.41.\x*, kodwa ingalungiselanga njalo ingenzanga ngokwentando yayo\x + 12.47.\x*, izatshaywa \add imivimvinya\add* eminengi\x + Dute. 25.2,3.\x*.
\v 48 Kodwa leyo\x + 12.41.\x* ebingayazi, yenza okufanele ukutshaywa\x + Levi 5.17. Nani 15.29,30. 1 Tim. 1.13.\x*, izatshaywa \add imivimvinya\add* emilutshwana\x + Roma 1.19,20; 2.14,15.\x*. Laye wonke ophiwe okunengi, kuzadingwa okunengi kuye\x + Mat. 25.15,29.\x*; lalowo ophathiswe okunengi, kuzabizwa kuye okungaphezulu\x + 12.20.\x*.
\s Izibonakaliso zezikhathi
\p
\v 49 Ngize ukuphosela umlilo emhlabeni\x + Mat. 3.11. Luka 12.51.\x*, futhi kuyini engikufisayo nxa usubasiwe\x + 1 Kho. 14.14.\x*?
\v 50 Kodwa ngilobhabhathizo engizabhabhathizwa ngalo\x + Mat. 20.22. Mark. 10.38.\x*, futhi\x + Mark. 10.32. Luka 9.51. Joha. 12.27.\x* ngicindezelwe\x + Seb. 18.5. Fil. 1.23.\x* kangakanani luze lupheleliswe\x + 22.16.\x*.
\v 51 Licabanga ukuthi ngize ukunika ukuthula emhlabeni yini\x + Mat. 10.34,35.Luka 12.49. Mat. 10.21.\x*? Hatshi bo, ngithi kini, kodwa kulalokhu ukwehlukana\x + Mat. 3.11. Luka 12.51.\x*.
\v 52 Ngoba kusukela khathesi abahlanu endlini yinye bazakwehlukana, abathathu bamelane lababili, lababili bamelane labathathu,
\v 53 bazakwehlukana, uyise amelane lendodana, lendodana imelane loyise; unina amelane lendodakazi, lendodakazi imelane lonina; uninazala amelane lomalokazana wakhe, lomalokazana amelane loninazala\x + Mika 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 54 Wasesithi lemaxukwini: Nxa libona iyezi\x + Mat. 16.2,3.\x* lisukuma entshonalanga\x + 1 Kho. 18.44.\x*, lihle lithi: Izulu liyabuya; futhi kube njalo.
\v 55 Njalo nxa \add libona\add* umoya weningizimu uphephetha, lithi: Lizatshisa; besekusenzakala\x + Mat. 20.12.\x*.
\v 56 Bazenzisi! Liyakwazi ukuhlola umumo wesibhakabhaka lowomhlaba; kodwa lesisikhathi kungani lingasihloli\x + Mat. 16.3.\x*?
\p
\v 57 Pho, kungani ukuthi lingahluleli lani lina uqobo lwenu okulungileyo\x + 21.30.\x*?
\v 58 Ngoba nxa usiya\x + 12.58,59, Mat. 5.25,26.\x* lomangalelene laye kumantshi\x + 12.13,14.\x*, endleleni yenza ubungcono ukuthi ukhululwe kuye; hlezi akudonsele kumahluleli, lomahluleli akunikele epholiseni, lepholisa likuphosele entolongweni.
\v 59 Ngithi kuwe, kawusoze waphuma khona, uze ubhadale lenhlamvu encane yemali yokucina.
